---
title: Chicken & Kumara Dhal with Garlic Flatbread Chips & Greek Yoghurt
description: No wonder dhal is the darling of Indian home cooking – it's nutritious, versatile, easy to make and brimming with flavour. Here, we're adding tender pieces of chicken, sweet roasted kumara and carrot, and crunchy garlic flatbread chips.
